==English==

===Etymology===
A contraction of [[some]] + [[more]], so called becasue they're meant to be so tasty you always want some more.

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A snack food made by combining [[graham]] crackers, [[marshmallow]]s (frequently toasted) and [[chocolate]], a typical camping fireside treat.

